 411:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/App/usbd_cdc_acm_if.c ****   *         This function will issue a NAK packet on any OUT packet received on
 412:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/App/usbd_cdc_acm_if.c ****   *         USB endpoint until exiting this function. If you exit this function
 413:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/App/usbd_cdc_acm_if.c ****   *         before transfer is complete on CDC interface (ie. using DMA controller)
 414:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/App/usbd_cdc_acm_if.c ****   *         it will result in receiving more data while previous ones are still
 415:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/App/usbd_cdc_acm_if.c ****   *         not sent.
 416:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/App/usbd_cdc_acm_if.c ****   *
 417:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/App/usbd_cdc_acm_if.c ****   * @param  Buf: Buffer of data to be received
